# DeckVault — TCG Collection Manager

Supported games: Yu-Gi-Oh, Pokemon, Digimon.

Goals: track collection, import/export (including file backup), multi-collection, anime side collection, proxy print, optional cloud sync (own account), shared collections with activity log.

## Product scope (current)

**In scope:** Auth (optional cloud), Collection views, Search/Quick Add, Import CSV/decklist, Export, Collection manager, Anime collection (local), Proxy print, Settings + **JSON backup/restore**, **Share / collection invites** (editor/viewer), **Activity log + undo** (simple card actions).

**Out of scope (removed):** Deck builder, Wishlist, Folders, Tags, Price history, Trading, Notifications, Phase 4 community, **Live realtime presence**.

## Roadmap (slim)

**Now:** Backup-by-file, polish collection UX, API safety (caps + rate limit), collab + activity.

**Later (optional):** Stats summaries, bulk edit beyond delete, binder virtualization, anime cloud sync.
